1 Be it enacted by the People of the State of Maine as follows:
2 Sec. 1. 24 MRSA §2908 is enacted to read:
3 §2908. Denial of patient access prohibited
4 A health care practitioner may not deny a patient access to health care services to be
5 performed by another health care practitioner when those services are within the lawful
6 scope of practice of the other health care practitioner.
7 SUMMARY
88 This bill prohibits a health care practitioner from denying a patient access to health care
99 services to be performed by another health care practitioner when those services are within
1100 the lawful scope of practice of the other health care practitioner.
